{
  "stem": "10572.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 18.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had a wonderful way of ultimately finding a way of killing you economically.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one day, they, in May 1938, they came into my father's office.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they confiscated, under some pretext, the steel files with all, with all the files and cards of our customers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my father told them that it was against his ethical concepts that there was a-- just like a physician would not talk and give the facts, that, that an ethical merchant would not reveal these facts.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they made it very clear to him that if he would refuse to turn those files over to him, that he would be under arrest and that our organization would be closed as of this moment.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my father had no choice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they took the steel files.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And about four days later-- and I have in my papers there a copy-- the Gestapo sent a letter to every one of our customers with a complete breakdown of what they had bought.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And if they felt that they had been overcharged, to contact the undersigned, Dr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Mercantaler, ?] who would then take care of the, of the over-pricing policies that this Jewish firm has been, has been suspected for, for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But there were-- just like we had during the war here in America, we had the OPA, the Office of Price Control.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That same thing existed in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was not a pin in our store that was over-priced.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were pope-ier than the Pope in, in, in sticking to the-- knowing that that's all.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But doing, by sending this letter out, first of all, appealing to the lowest instincts in customers-- you know, if somebody owed us $1,000, my gosh, if I say, maybe I can get rid of this debt.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The fantastic thing was not one of our customers complained about our, of having been over-priced.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But we knew then that this was the death knell and that we had to throw the towel in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And, and my father-- and when I looked back, in, in a spirit of complete straightforwardness and honesty, went, after three days after these letters were mailed, went to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I went with him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He asked me to go with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we sat down with Inspector [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Zichting. ?] Inspector [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Zichting ?] was the head of the Gestapo in Hildesheim.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father asked him, could we have the files back?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, yes, you can.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father looked at [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Zichting ?] and said to him, Herr Inspektor, after seeing these files, you will now understand why I felt I had to protect the names of my customers.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Zichting ?] looked the other way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know at that time why my father said that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Among the files was [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Zichting's ?] father-in-law.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And by the time we got the files back, [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Zichting's ?] father-in-law's file was gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was this kind of lack of fear that I would constantly see in my father, I was somehow brought up with that, that you don't cave in in the, in the light of injustice and so on.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that was then we asked for permission to liquidate our business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That picture, that picture was taken two days before the liquidation sale started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And since we had carried very exclusive lines, and you know, like Burberry, and so on, we could not have windows decorated with the, with prices to entice people to come in.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father had the idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he asked our window trimmer to trim the most beautiful windows he had ever trimmed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to have windows by color.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a brown window and a blue window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and he said, and we will not have any prices on the merchandise, because people trust us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They trust us for our integrity and honesty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we will not try to impress them with prices, because even, even with our prices, we couldn't entice people who wanted bargains.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that is how then the liquidation sale started.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
